<P>Lord Cromwel's hand in Henry's marriage wit<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> the immediately di&s;liked prince&s;s of Cleves, lo&s;t hi<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> his wonted favour. The duke of Norfolk feared hi<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> oppo&s;ing of Henry's marriage with mi&s;s Howard
